# CampusRoute Phase 1 - Chatbot

## Objective
Implement a basic AI-powered chatbot to provide real-time bus information for students and parents.

## Features
- Google Vertex AI (Gemini LLM) integration
- Text-based query interface
- Real-time bus status, ETA, and schedule info
- Incident reporting (bus delays, breakdowns)
- Streamlit interface with ngrok tunneling for public access

## Installation
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
